<div class="">
<div class="project--header">
<h1>Spring Cloud Bus</h1>
<span class="version label current">3.0 0-M3</span>
<div class="social-links">
<a class="link--github" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/spring-cloud/spring-cloud-bus">
